comment: /**  * Execute a handshake request to the given url and handle the resulting  * WebSocket session with the given handler.  * @param url the handshake url  * @param handler the handler of the WebSocket session  * @return completion {@code Mono<Void>} to indicate the outcome of the  * WebSocket session handling.  */
code: /**  * Execute a handshake request to the given url and handle the resulting  * WebSocket session with the given handler.  * @param url the handshake url  * @param handler the handler of the WebSocket session  * @return completion {@code Mono<Void>} to indicate the outcome of the  * WebSocket session handling.  */ Mono<Void> execute(URI url, WebSocketHandler handler).

comment: /**  * A variant of {@link #execute(URI, WebSocketHandler)} with custom headers.  * @param url the handshake url  * @param headers custom headers for the handshake request  * @param handler the handler of the WebSocket session  * @return completion {@code Mono<Void>} to indicate the outcome of the  * WebSocket session handling.  */
code: /**  * A variant of {@link #execute(URI, WebSocketHandler)} with custom headers.  * @param url the handshake url  * @param headers custom headers for the handshake request  * @param handler the handler of the WebSocket session  * @return completion {@code Mono<Void>} to indicate the outcome of the  * WebSocket session handling.  */ Mono<Void> execute(URI url, HttpHeaders headers, WebSocketHandler handler).
